{"tid":1822622,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"習近平因香港一子錯滿盤皆落索 本來佢可以係統一台灣既「民族英雄」，但依家基本上係千古罪人","createTime":"2020-01-13T05:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T07:11:57.000Z","uid":251052,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1c1095bd908f1931a30ef20e45939f1a632776ef","tid":1822622,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻小學生本來想統一台灣 做共產黨歷史上最偉大既領袖甚至超越毛澤東<br />\n<br />\n但就係行錯咗一步 變成千古罪人 貿易戰比美國打到得返半條命 香港台灣覺醒 <br />\n依家仲有豬瘟鼠疫武漢肺炎 <br />\n天時地利人和全部都企係佢對面<br />\n<br />\n依家可能係最接近共產黨滅黨既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9e123f7ce3af2448631ce61285a7fb0a2ed303","tid":1822622,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:22:31.000Z","msg":"咁就好"},{"pid":"deb3a7e008656c8db3ff41792ec277e7f5ec6f31","tid":1822622,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:23:49.000Z","msg":"佢大心急啦.."},{"pid":"6cffdeaf4e3d5ac5ac5b4f2e3d842bb85b31a4d8","tid":1822622,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deb3a7e008656c8db3ff41792ec277e7f5ec6f31","tid":1822622,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:23:49.000Z","msg":"佢大心急啦.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:23:59.000Z","msg":"太"},{"pid":"9d02c68c2743521ee9a3826ac03768621bf6e043","tid":1822622,"uid":134415,"like":9,